{"tid":206752,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人對日本戰國有興趣??","createTime":"2017-04-18T14:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T06:56:44.000Z","uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0214e487b0a2269fb15cf69be74cb10cfb8b14","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"依排睇咗啲關於日本戰國嘅書，發現到日本戰國統一嘅難度唔會比德國差，但係好少人關注，所以想試下同大家分享。如果有人想睇嘅話我先開始打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c50749ac886b31e4fe11cf4c53ac0fe6011da2","tid":206752,"uid":12752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bbc8fcb3c21175b662fb44f91eef76eea3f144","tid":206752,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"信長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c3c0d9a7110d4395d9064e07fa834fa582076f","tid":206752,"uid":12961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T14:52:47.000Z","msg":"留名聽戰國歷史"},{"pid":"745459624473f18fb2413583857869c310e1f120","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"你問我答系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問岩我唔識既勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddef7eb51af93c5568129b147183ba44fcb5066","tid":206752,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你問我答系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問岩我唔識既勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本第一個統一全國既係咪信長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1793873b53b44058ab2309886d187e21015aef9","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你問我答系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問岩我唔識既勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本第一個統一全國既係咪信長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n信長無統一到全國<br />\n日本戰國係封建制 根本係可能統一到<br />\n只可能令全國名臣服於自己<br />\n真正意義上統一日本既天下人係豐臣秀吉"},{"pid":"3996fa65d55794b0f63c091b4c5a4885c9a34b33","tid":206752,"uid":90589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"玩無雙既時候真田幸村成個趙雲咁好型好巴炮，其實史實點？"},{"pid":"38936f4de3231d394292244745e5f8b6917b1eae","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你問我答系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問岩我唔識既勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本第一個統一全國既係咪信長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n信長無統一到全國<br />\n日本戰國係封建制 根本<span style=\"color: red;\">無</span>可能統一到<br />\n只可能令全國名臣服於自己<br />\n真正意義上統一日本既天下人係豐臣秀吉</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd9c47a15a5163e14355299b528e86bd854996fd","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩無雙既時候真田幸村成個趙雲咁好型好巴炮，其實史實點？</blockquote><br />\n原名係真田信繁 真田幸村只不過係通稱<br />\n綽號日本第一兵 譽為日本三大悲劇人物<br />\n上田城之戰玩死德川秀忠<br />\n大阪之陣爭d迫死家康<br />\n都真係幾把炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8c49fe6599dc3dfb9929cbd6679452e7ec4e87","tid":206752,"uid":42332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"Lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e7f8d1581df03ba832ad58e79cdd2dc98a3e23","tid":206752,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime