00Z","msg":"其實日本戰國 似唔似 三國咁 會用計謀打贏杖<br />\n有既講啲黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6149cb7f29b4ffe882b86253fe275b43c5e951b6","tid":206752,"uid":33941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"709ae399920d1e90d656d29ae2e3b32d021f315d","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實日本戰國 似唔似 三國咁 會用計謀打贏杖<br />\n有既講啲黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對有<br />\n舉兩個例子 <br />\n織田信長係桶狹間之戰，以伏兵奇襲既奇謀 擊敗數倍於己既今川義元<br />\n竹中半兵衛以16人之力 智取當時難攻不落既稻葉山城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600f4c21a36b41587f0aa18679080d69ebec562a","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T22:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c4e2ab087e2f7c2a5ee54ff2018a624eee7380","tid":206752,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T23:24:33.000Z","msg":"有無咩書/劇有哂個統一流程?<br />\n或者巴打簡單講下?"},{"pid":"d51ba5e14005c38d62abeb779d56ceabcb417fed","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T00:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無咩書/劇有哂個統一流程?<br />\n或者巴打簡單講下?</blockquote><br />\n最簡單咁講<br />\n經過數十年合戰<br />\n織田信長堀起後 將近統一日本之際被明智光秀殺害<br />\n然後秀吉擊敗光秀 柴田勝家 北條氏政等等敵對大名統一日本<br />\n死後德川家康同石田三成等豐臣家殘餘勢力爭天下<br />\n最尾家康消滅豐臣紙 建立江戶時代"},{"pid":"c39a8947cfd579735be7356e7d649e417c8e050b","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269f3d10c7eade6a22564d75a286af4ca570e9f8","tid":206752,"uid":23026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"其實有巴打開post講日本戰國史<br />\n［日本戰國史］關東英傑傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/156373/page/13?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/156373/page/13?ref=ios </a>"},{"pid":"b5ca69965b3b9f4308a27a051760e8f15a7f126e","tid":206752,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"好少人關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港絕對唔少<br />\n人哋post都講咗幾個喇喎"},{"pid":"fd9213a7c85ad80441cca80d398c98b3d1bdc6b1","tid":206752,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3920815c54020d17359b5f567053f2bbed7ff4","tid":206752,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無咩書/劇有哂個統一流程?<br />\n或者巴打簡單講下?</blockquote><br />\n最簡單咁講<br />\n經過數十年合戰<br />\n織田信長堀起後 將近統一日本之際被明智光秀殺害<br />\n然後秀吉擊敗光秀 柴田勝家 北條氏政等等敵對大名統一日本<br />\n死後德川家康同石田三成等豐臣家殘餘勢力爭天下<br />\n最尾家康消滅豐臣紙 建立江戶時代</blockquote><br />\n德川執返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa9c840b3576850c06d9a0caa0a33add1a9cd54","tid":206752,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實日本戰國 似唔似 三國咁 會用計謀打贏杖<br />\n有既講啲黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絕對有<br />\n舉兩個例子 <br />\n織田信長係桶狹間之戰，以伏兵奇襲既奇謀 擊敗數倍於己既今川義元<br />\n竹中半兵衛以16人之力 智取當時難攻不落既稻葉山城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好睇 但問題佢地戰爭較小型"},{"pid":"7c66292ab8221509fd72f9c7f54267b17b0f832a","tid":206752,"uid":23315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排睇緊真田丸，好正<img src=\"/assets/fa